<h2>ABOUT</h2>
<p>ASAPVALENTINE is an aspiring artist wishing to become a tattoo artist. Currently studying graphic design in university while simultaneously working on his tattoo apprentice portfolio. ASAPVALENTINE experienced many art oppportunities such as going to a prestigious visual and performing arts high school, recognized and winning a gold key in the Scholastic Art and Writing Awards of 2018 in photography, an intern of the Work of Art program from 2017-2019, and a brief summer graphic design internship at Dailey and Associates in West Hollywood.  </p>
</main>

